<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #f4f7fb; }
    .wrapper { background: white; margin: 20px auto; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #11998e 0%, #38ef7d 100%); color: white; padding: 35px 30px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
    .header p  { margin: 8px 0 0; opacity: 0.9; font-size: 14px; }
    .content   { padding: 30px; }
    .detail-box { background: #f0fff4; border: 1px solid #c6f6d5; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .detail-box-neutral { background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .info-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; font-size: 14px; }
    .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .label { color: #666; }
    .value { font-weight: bold; color: #333; }
    .total-highlight { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #11998e, #38ef7d); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; }
    .total-highlight .amount { font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; margin: 8px 0; }
    .total-highlight .date   { font-size: 16px; opacity: 0.9; }
    .attachment-note { background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fde68a; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px; font-size: 13px; color: #92400e; margin: 15px 0; }
    .footer { background: #2d3748; color: #ccc; padding: 20px 30px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; }
    .footer strong { color: white; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>✅ Votre salaire a été payé !</h1>
        <p>INTEGRA RH — Système de Gestion des Ressources Humaines</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Bonjour <strong>{{ salaire.user.username }}</strong>,</p>
        <p>
            Excellente nouvelle ! Votre salaire du mois de
            <strong>{{ salaire.datePaiement|date('F Y') }}</strong>
            a été <strong>versé avec succès</strong>.
        </p>

        <div class="total-highlight">
            <div style="font-size:13px; opacity:0.9;">💳 Montant versé</div>
            <div class="amount">{{ salaire.totalAmount|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} DT</div>
            <div class="date">le {{ salaire.datePaiement|date('d/m/Y') }}</div>
        </div>

        <div class="detail-box">
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="label">Salaire de base: </span>
                <span class="value">{{ salaire.baseAmount|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} DT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="label">Bonus total: </span>
                <span class="value" style="color:#28a745;">{{ salaire.bonusAmount|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} DT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="label">Mode de paiement: </span>
                <span class="value">Virement bancaire</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <span class="label">Statut: </span>
                <span class="value" style="color:#28a745;">✅ PAYÉ</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        {% if salaire.bonusRules|length > 0 %}
        <div class="detail-box-neutral">
            <p style="margin:0 0 10px; font-weight:bold; font-size:13px;">⭐ Primes et bonus appliqués :</p>
            {% for rule in salaire.bonusRules %}
                {% if rule.status == 'ACTIVE' %}
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="label">{{ rule.nomRegle }}: </span>
                    <span class="value" style="color:#667eea;">{{ rule.percentage }}% → + {{ rule.bonus|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} DT</span>
                </div>
                {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="attachment-note">
            📎 <strong>Votre fiche de paie complète est jointe à cet email.</strong><br>
            Elle contient tous les détails de votre rémunération pour ce mois.
        </div>

        <p style="color:#666; font-size:13px;">
            Merci pour votre travail et votre engagement ! 💼
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <strong>INTEGRA RH</strong><br>
        Cet email a été envoyé automatiquement, merci de ne pas y répondre.
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>